Everyone, we don't normally get personal here, but many of us just lost a good friend. 

Jared Sandifer, also known as Republican Jesus, Derek Zoolander Center For Tea Party Patriots and other liberal pages, has kept us entertained for a number of years.

Sandifer was a good guy who cared about everyone and everything. He also spent a lot of time "trolling" Republicans because that's what he did best. If a conservative did or said something stupid, he was there (In other words, it was almost a full time job for him).

Not much is known about the circumstances of his passing, but one thing is for certain -- the liberal world lost a good person who spent much of his time fighting against the hatred espoused by the Right with humor, snark, and a fair bit of sarcasm.

Jared, you will be missed, and we love you.
